<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.1.1">
<l>vāṭiṉēṉ vāṭi varuntiṉēṉ maṉattāl</l>
<l>peruntuya riṭumpaiyil piṟantu</l>
<l>kūṭiṉēṉ kūṭi yiḷaiyavart tammēā</l>
<l>ṭavarttaruṅ kalaviyē karuti</l>
<l>ōṭiṉēṉ ōṭi yuyvatōrp poruḷā</l>
<l>luṇarveṉum perumpatam tirintu</l>
<l>nāṭiṉēṉ nāṭi nāṉkaṇṭu koṇṭēṉ</l>
<l>nārā yaṇāveṉṉum nāmam.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I languished; languishing, I suffered in my mind.</l>
<l rend="indent">Being born into a sorrow of great grief,</l>
<l>I joined [it]. Having joined with young women,</l>
<l rend="indent">thinking only of the embraces they give,</l>
<l>I ran; running, wandering the great path called ‘knowledge’</l>
<l rend="indent">by [means of] one thing,</l>
<l>I searched for escape; searching, I discovered for myself</l>
<l rend="indent">the name which is pronounced “Nārāyaṇā!”</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
